{{wikipediapar|Suitheism}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Coined by American occultists [[w:David Michael Cunningham|David Michael Cunningham]] and Traeonna A. R. Wagener, from {{Lat}} ''[[sui]]'' ("of oneself") and [[theism]].

===Noun===
'''suitheism'''
# the [[belief]] that one is a [[god]]; but that there may be others

